high_descs: Turn around and head across the room, take a left at the toaster then walk to the dishwasher on the left of the fridge
Pick up the fork that is sitting on the dishwasher in front of the coffee machine
Take a step to the left and face the right corner of the white table to the left of the dishwasher
Place the fork in the chalice that's on the right.  The one that is slightly close to you
Pick up the chalice that contains the fork
Turn right and walk to the dishwasher and turn left to face the dishwasher
Place the chalice on top the dishwasher to the left of the coffee machine and right of the knife
anns.task_desc: Place a chalice containing a fork on top of a dishwasher

high_descs: Turn around and walk through the kitchen, to the dishwasher on your left.
Pick up the fork in front of the coffee maker.
Turn to the white table on your right.
Place the fork in the gold wine glass beside the apple
Pick up the gold wine glass with the fork inside it.
Turn back to the dishwasher on your right.
Put the gold wine glass with the fork inside it on the back, right corner of the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Put a wine glass containing a fork on the dish washer.

high_descs: Turn around and face the brown table by the fridge on your left.
Take the fork off of the table in front of you.
Turn left and face the white table on your right.
Place the fork in the cup on the table in front of you.
Take the cup with the fork off of the table in front of you.
Turn right and face the brown table on the left by the fridge.
Place the cup with the fork on the brown table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a fork on the table by the fridge.
